<h2>Restaurant Upgrade</h2>
<p>For an even more refined version:</p>
<ul>
<<<<<<< HEAD
  <li>Brown 2 tablespoons of butter and stir it in just before serving.</li>
  <li>Add 1/2 teaspoon lobster base (such as Better Than Bouillon Lobster Base) if your seafood stock needs more lobster flavor.</li>
  <li>Finish with a few drops of sherry vinegar instead of additional lemon juice for a brighter, more balanced finish.</li>
</ul>
